long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
Google Voice For PC, Windows, and Mac chrome theme can easily change your New chrome Tab Color and New tab background.
You can easily change your New Tab Color by using this Google Voice for pc New Tab chrome extension.

It's simple and replaces your current Chrome New Tab window with Google Voice For PC, Windows and Mac - New Tab Chrome Theme. This chrome theme extension only developed for Google Voice app users FAN.
